                <head>No. 257.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Frelinghuysen</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hoppin</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-10-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 30, 1883</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Frelinghuysen instructed Mr. Hoppin to ascertain and telegraph the regiment
                    in which O’Donnell had served, or the name of the captain of his company.</p>
            </div>
